1.0.name: wordpress/jquery-drop-down-menu-plugin
1.0.description:
theme header.php or where you want to display menu. Configuration: Options » Jquery Drop Down Menu. JQuery Drop Down Menu plugin can manage Multi-level dropdown menu, plus you can customize the menu with full animation support and many more from admin area,

You can find the plugin DEMO here.
